[{"catalog_class_code":"0100","catalog_part_number":"0010","catalog_option":"Option: 1 &nbsp;(Bundle)","catalog_checkbox":"&check;","catalog_checkbox_description":"","catalog_bin_loc":"","catalog_description":"Branch with Pay-Per-Click","catalog_specs":"<p>Building a generational branch is the starting point. &nbsp;All options are applied to a branch.</p><br><br><ol><li>Configure Branch Architechture</li><li>Implement Branch Photo</li><li>Type Branch Narrative</li><li>Configure Branch Descendants</li><li>Display Branch Profile</li><li>Display Branch Descendant Names</li><li>Configure <strong><i>Family Tree</i></strong> Link to Display Branch Narrative in <strong><i>Isolated View</i></strong></li></ol>","catalog_price":"<p><span class='money-color'>$125.00</span> <i>(configure and build branch)</i><br><br><span class='money-color'>$15.00</span> Pay Per Click (Per Descendant)</p>","catalog_price_frequency":"<ul><li>Per Generational Branch</li><li>Generational Branch Narrative Limited to <strong><i>200</i></strong> Words.</li><li>Up to 3 narrative revisions allowed before additional <span class='money-color'>$10.00</span> charge due.</li><li>If the generational branch head or descendant is Deceased, the following fields are also Displayed:<br><br><ol><li>An Asterisk (*) Indicating Deceased</li><li>Year Died, and Age at Death</li> </ol></li></ul>","catalog_active":"y"},{"catalog_class_code":"0100","catalog_part_number":"0020","catalog_option":"Option: 2 &nbsp;(After Branch PPC)","catalog_checkbox":"&check;","catalog_checkbox_description":"","catalog_bin_loc":"","catalog_description":"Add Pay-Per-Click","catalog_specs":"<p><u>If</u> you built a generational branch without bundling Pay-Per-Click, the only way to do now is at a higher price.<br></p><br><br><ol><li>Enable Descendant (Pay Per Click)</li><li>Display Descendant Profile on Click</li></ol>","catalog_price":"<p><span class='money-color'>$20.00</span></p>","catalog_price_frequency":"<ul><li>Per Descendant Click.</